      • query

        public ActivityReport query(Context context,
                   ActivityReport request)
                     throws ApplicationException
        从接口复制的说明: ActivityReportService
        The retailer may consult the activity reports on their terminal, pls refer to TE interface document '#4.7.8 Activity Report' for more information.
        指定者:
        query 在接口中 ActivityReportService
        request - The request object, fields 'beginTime' and 'endTime' must be set.
        返回:
        a activity report.
        抛出:
        ApplicationException - when encounter any application exception.

      • verifyTimeCriteria

        protected void verifyTimeCriteria(Context context,
                      ActivityReport request)
                           throws ApplicationException
        Check the query criteria, includes:
        • startTime must be earlier than endTime.
        • startTime can't be earlier than max allowed querying days.
        抛出:
        ApplicationException
